# F&O Phoenix API
Universal API for Frank & Oak.

# Group Customers

Customers related resources of the **F&O Phoenix API**


Attributes
- `id` - Customer's ID
- `created_at` - UTC timestamp ([ISO 8601](http://www.w3.org/TR/NOTE-datetime)) for when this object was created
- `updated_at` - UTC timestamp ([ISO 8601](http://www.w3.org/TR/NOTE-datetime)) for last time this object was updated - *optional*
- `group_id` - Customer's group
- `email` - Customer's Email Address
- `first_name` - Customer's first name
- `last_name` - Customer's last name
- `gender` - Customer's gender (male or female) - *optional*
- `birthdate` - Customer's birthdate - *optional*
- `id_hash` - Customer's encrypted ID hash
- `default_shipping_address_id` - Customer's default shipping address ID - *optional*
- `default_billing_address_id` - Customer's default billing address ID - *optional*
- `store_credit` - Customer's Store Credit (can't be updated from here)
- `facebook_id` - Customer's facebook ID - *optional*
- `google_id` - Customer's google ID - *optional*
- `style` - Customer's style (casual, dressy, etc.) - *optional*
- `shirt_size` - Customer's shirt size (XL, L...) - *optional*
- `pants_size` - Customer's pants_size (30, 32...) - *optional*
- `blazer_size` - Customer's blazer size (40R, 42R...) - *optional*
- `shoe_size` - Customer's shoe size (10, 11...) - *optional*
- `default_currency` - Customer's default Currency (associated to website_id)
- `is_hc_member` - Is the member Hunt Club (use groupe_id == 4 for now)
- `is_first_time_buyer` - Has Customer purchased anything before? Related to Order history


