# Group Products

Attributes
- `id` - Product ID
- `created_at` - UTC timestamp ([ISO 8601](http://www.w3.org/TR/NOTE-datetime)) for when this object was created
- `updated_at` - UTC timestamp ([ISO 8601](http://www.w3.org/TR/NOTE-datetime)) for last time this object was updated - *Optional*
- `sku` - The sku of the configurable product
- `name` - Full name
- `description` - Description of the product
- `short_description` - Short description of the product - *Optional*
- `new_from_date` - Starting UTC timestamp ([ISO 8601](http://www.w3.org/TR/NOTE-datetime)) when product is considered as new - *Optional*
- `new_to_date` - Ending UTC timestamp ([ISO 8601](http://www.w3.org/TR/NOTE-datetime)) when product is considered as new - *Optional*
- `required_options` - Does the product require sizes? (if not, can add directly to cart for example)
- `has_options` - Does the product have sizes? 
- `price` - Original price
- `special_price` - Discounted price - *Optional*
- `special_from_date` - Starting UTC timestamp ([ISO 8601](http://www.w3.org/TR/NOTE-datetime)) when product is on sale - *Optional*
- `special_to_date` - Ending UTC timestamp ([ISO 8601](http://www.w3.org/TR/NOTE-datetime)) when product is on sale - *Optional*
- `tier_price` - Tier price (e.g. Buy 1 at original price, but buy 3 and get a discount) - *Optional*
- `tier_price_qty` - Quantity required for tier price elligibility - *Optional*
- `hc_price` - Hunt Club Customer Group price (group id == 4 e.g.) - *Optional*
- `gift_message_available` - Message to be added to the product - *Optional*
- `gift_wrapping_available` - Wrapping to be added to the product - *Optional*
- `gift_wrapping_price` - Wrapping price - *Optional*
- `image_urls` - A list of image urls of the category


